---
title: Hoisin Pork Meatball Rice Bowls  with Bok Choy and DIY Chili Peanuts
description: Juicy pork meatballs seasoned like your favourite dumplings are served over fragrant jasmine rice, paired with tender bok choy and finished with a drizzle of homemade chili peanuts for the perfect balance of heat and flavour. Simple, satisfying, and addictive!

